mean_max_m_ws <- weather %>% group_by(years,months) %>% summarise(ws_m_mean = mean(.., na.rm = TRUE))
numofNA <- dim(weather[which(is.na(weather$..)), c('date', '..')])[1]
for (i in seq(numofNA)) {
  year <- as.character(weather[which(is.na(weather$..)), c('years','months', '..')][1,1])
  month <- as.character(weather[which(is.na(weather$..)), c('years','months', '..')][1,2])
  weather[which(is.na(weather$..)), '..'][1] <- as.vector(unlist(mean_max_m_ws[which(mean_max_m_ws$years == year & mean_max_m_ws$months == month), 'ws_m_mean']))
}

cv_allmodel <- function(x, y){
  set.seed(1234)
  folds <- createFolds(analysis_data2$, k=x)
  nb_acc <- c()
  mn_acc <- c()
  nn_acc <- c()
    for (f in folds) {
    train_cv <- analysis_data2[-f,]
    test_cv <- analysis_data2[f, ]
    cv.real_val <- test_cv$
    test_cv <- dplyr::select(test_cv, -c(""))
    cv.nb_model <- naiveBayes(~., data=train_cv, laplace=1)
    cv.mn_model <- multinom(~., data=train_cv, trace=F)
    cv.nn_model <- nnet(~., data = train_cv, size=y, maxit=1000, trace=F)
    cv.pred_nb <- predict(cv.nb_model, test_cv, type="class")
    cv.pred_mn <- predict(cv.mn_model, test_cv, type="class")
    cv.pred_nn <- predict(cv.nn_model, test_cv, type="class")
    nb_f_acc <- sum(cv.pred_nb==cv.real_val)/NROW(cv.real_val)
    mn_f_acc <- sum(cv.pred_mn==cv.real_val)/NROW(cv.real_val)
    nn_f_acc <- sum(cv.pred_nn==cv.real_val)/NROW(cv.real_val)
    nb_acc <-append(nb_acc, nb_f_acc)
    mn_acc <-append(mn_acc, mn_f_acc)
    nn_acc <-append(nn_acc, nn_f_acc)
    }
  cv.df <- data.frame(
    k = seq(1,x),
    naive_Bayes = nb_acc,
    multinomial = mn_acc,
    neuralnet = nn_acc
  )
  return(cv.df)
}
